	<p>It's quite possible that the choice of Furor was a bad one, as Korask said, only time will tell.<br />
<br />
The concept is encouraging, though.  They hired someone who indisputably gives a **** about what kind of game he's playing.  If SoE had done this early on, I don't think so many of us, myself included, would be crying in our beer over the state of the game.  At least not for the same reasons.</p>
	
	
	
